+	 **======================================================================*
+	 ** 4-bit      | 16-bit  | 4-bit  | 8-bit        | 32-bit       | 12-bit *
+	 **=====================================================================*/
+
+	/* VLAN (BD) Hash table action entry map:*
+	 **=======================================*
+	 ** [07:00]         - forward port list
+	 ** [15:08]         - untag list
+	 ** [18:16]         - ucast_hit_action
+	 ** [21:19]         - mcast_hit_action
+	 ** [24:22]         - ucast_miss_action
+	 ** [27:25]         - mcast_miss_action
